<div class='flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full'>
<section class="highlight-box marketing">
  <header>
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">
      Readers, writers, and forgetful academics...
    </h2>
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-align-center rejoice mt-4 mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">REJOICE!</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="flex flex-row">
    <p class='w-4/5'>
      <strong class='brand'>
      Highlighter</strong> saves your notable quotes, or "highlights," 
      while reading in your favorite web browser.
      Your highlights are always available online to reference whenever you need them.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-row">
      <p class='flex w-1/3 justify-center'>
        <%= link_to 'save', '', class: 'text-xs text-purple-300' %>
        <%= link_to 'with', '', class: 'text-xs text-purple-300' %>
        <%= link_to 'tags', '', class: 'text-xs text-purple-300' %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="highlight-box">
  <div class="video-box">
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SIxied7AVHg" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</section>

<section class='highlight-box text-align-center'>
  <h3 class='text-align-center no-margin-top underline box-header'>Download the beta version</h3>
  <p>Hi, friend! The user experience is a little bumpy at the moment, 
  but don't fret&mdash;your data will be safe and private.
  In the meantime, <a href="mailto:smcalilly@gmail.com">please report</a> 
  any bugs or suggestions for improvement.
  </p>
  <%= link_to(image_tag('firefox-badge.png', alt: 'Download for Firefox'), 
    'https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/highlighter-online', 
      class: 'download', id: 'firefox') 
  %>
  <%= link_to(image_tag('chrome-badge-small.png', alt: 'Download for Chrome'), 
    'https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/highlighter/jhbdfidbplpijoncnlfooepldoleioga', 
      class: 'download', id: 'chrome') 
  %>
  <div class='text-align-center margin-top'>
    <p>Don't see your browser? <a href='https://forms.gle/EWhFUiKtR5QgzuRZ7' target="_blank">Request a download.</a></p>
    
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="highlight-box">
    <h3 class="text-align-center no-margin-top underline box-header">About the Author</h3>
    <%= image_tag 'sam-n-okie.jpeg', class: 'sam-n-okie', alt: 'the author and his dog', title: 'sam and okie man' %>
    <p>
      Highlighter was built by me, Sam McAlilly. I'm a writer
      who needs something like this for reading and researching.
      I'm also a programmer.
    </p>
    <p>
      I suspect this might be useful for actual academics and journalists, 
      so I'm sharing it. I'm working to expand this core functionality.
      The next update will include the ability to add notes and tags to the highlights.
      I'm also going to combine this with 
      <a href="https://medium.com/@smcalilly/project-gutenberg-typography-tool-55c9652d11fa" target="_blank" style="font-family: verdana">
      another browser extension</a> I built, which improves the reading experience 
      for websites with bad typopgraphy. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Please tell your friends if you find this useful
      and don't hesitate to <a href="mailto:smcalilly@gmail.com">email me</a> 
      with any suggestions on how to improve it.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-align-center no-margin-bottom rejoice">Keep on reading!</h2>
  </section>
</div>